we were wrong.

590
00:24:07,519 --> 00:24:09,240
We almost delayed your important business.

591
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:10,680
It won't happen again.

592
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,240
No, no, definitely not.

593
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:15,279
Tomorrow, there's still work, right?

594
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,920
We will definitely work hard.

595
00:24:17,119 --> 00:24:17,599
Definitely work hard.

596
00:24:17,599 --> 00:24:19,359
San'er, this, this, this...

