San'er, you forgot.

599
00:24:21,759 --> 00:24:23,279
This group said they want to raise the price.

600
00:24:23,279 --> 00:24:24,319
You can't take them.

601
00:24:24,599 --> 00:24:25,480
Don't take us.

602
00:24:25,599 --> 00:24:26,480
You said it before.

603
00:24:26,599 --> 00:24:28,240
If this delivery doesn't arrive, we'll lose 500 yuan.

604
00:24:28,279 --> 00:24:29,519
