606
00:24:30,559 --> 00:24:31,279
Don't listen to her nonsense.

607
00:24:31,359 --> 00:24:32,440
How am I talking nonsense? You said it.

608
00:24:32,519 --> 00:24:33,200
I can testify.

609
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,440
It was Tan Hong who said it.

610
00:24:34,599 --> 00:24:35,839
She even asked us to give her two yuan.

611
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:36,880
What are you saying?

612
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:38,039
Why are you hitting people?

613
00:24:38,119 --> 00:24:39,200
You can't hit people. You can't hit people.

614
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,000
I'll tear your mouth apart.

615
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:40,519
I'll beat you to death.

616
00:24:40,559 --> 00:24:41,119
That's enough.

617
00:24:43,799 --> 00:24:45,160
Second sister-in-law, go back to the room first.

618
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:46,279
You can't listen to them.

619
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:46,920
Go back.

620
00:24:48,119 --> 00:24:49,000
This, this...

621
00:24:55,839 --> 00:24:57,480
Since everyone thinks two yuan is too little

622
00:24:57,759 --> 00:24:58,440
then forget it.

623
00:24:59,240 --> 00:24:59,960
No, it's not too little, not too little.

624
00:25:00,079 --> 00:25:01,519
Don't go, let's discuss it further.

625
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:02,640
