627
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:04,519
Third Brother

628
00:25:04,799 --> 00:25:06,920
We can still talk about these two yuan.

629
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,240
Yes, yes, right.

630
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:10,039
This matter is reasonable and fair.

631
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:11,720
It's beneficial for everyone.

632
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,000
We are all from the same village.

633
00:25:13,039 --> 00:25:14,480
Is it meaningful to do this repeatedly?

634
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:15,519
Is it meaningful?

635
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:16,599
I promise

636
00:25:16,839 --> 00:25:18,480
In the future, we will definitely work hard.

637
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,319
We won't mess around anymore.

638
00:25:20,799 --> 00:25:22,200
Yes, yes, I promise too.

639
00:25:25,799 --> 00:25:26,319
Alright then.

640
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:28,599
If anyone causes trouble again

641
00:25:29,039 --> 00:25:30,240
