644
00:25:33,279 --> 00:25:34,680
No objections, no objections, no objections.

645
00:25:34,759 --> 00:25:36,039
Then let's sign, sign, sign.

646
00:25:36,119 --> 00:25:36,759
Come on, sign it.

647
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:38,160
Hurry up, sign it.

648
00:25:39,119 --> 00:25:40,400
Come on, you sign first, you sign first.
